\series bold 
The Inevitability of Uncertainty
\series default 
 
\layout Standard

In common terminology there are three kinds of "errors": (1) mistakes or
 human errors, (2) systematic errors due to measurement or equipment problems
 and (3) inherent uncertainties.
\layout Standard


